PHP 7
=====

Tag names following PHP version.
Based on images from [leandrosilva/php](https://hub.docker.com/r/leandrosilva/php/).

Branches
--------
- 7.1-apache
- 7.1-cli
- 7.1-fpm
- 7.1-fpm-alpine
- 7.0-apache
- 7.0-cli
- 7.0-fpm
- 7.0-fpm-alpine

To use the latest php version available for a branch, use:
```
docker pull leandrosilva/php-ci:7.0-apache
```

Tools installed
---------------

- phpunit
- phpmd
- pdepend
- phpcpd
- php_codesniffer
- phpdox
- phploc
- phpcb
- phing
- codeception

